1. This song is based on a real event that must have happened to Anthony hence why his songs have such strong lyrics
2. Liza and Anthony never actually kissed, they acted it out
3. Jasmine isn't in this because this was before Anthony and Jaz got together/ ever met
4. This song is about how a girl played with Anthony's feelings and he wanted a real relationship whilst the girl didn't
5. Mind Over Matter was the idea of how it didn't matter about the intercourse it mattered about the love the 'mind' is technically the brain and the heart telling that person that they love the other one. The 'matter' is the current activity. Hence why Anthony says 'Mind Over Matter' and not 'Matter Over Mind'
6. Liza and David broke up nearly 2 years ago so like stop.


So STOP complaining about how Anthony is 'cheating' on Jasmine when he's only acting for the sake of the video. Liza and Anthony don't have that type of relationship; they're just friends. Anthony loves Jasmine and no one else in that lovey-dovey way. So stop complaining that Jasmine wasn't in it, it's a video showing real stories about Anthony and Liza was just there to help portray his story. So if you have a problem with it, dislike the video and don't watch it OR just IGNORE it and move on with your lives without complaining about it! It's ANTHONY'S video and views, NOT YOURS. Thank you.
